<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>System Home Pet — Sistema de Gestão para Pet Shops e Clínicas Veterinárias</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,300;1,400&display=swap"
          rel="stylesheet"/>
    <style>
        /* ============================================================
        DESIGN TOKENS — LIGHT MODE (Cores alteradas para #5d57f4)
        ============================================================ */
        :root {
            --teal: #5d57f4;
            --teal-dark: #4a45c7;
            --teal-light: #efeeff;
            --teal-glow: rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.14);
            --accent: #F59E0B;
            --accent-light: #FEF3C7;
            --bg-base: #F8FAFC;
            --bg-alt: #FFFFFF;
            --bg-subtle: #F1F5F9;
            --surface-card: #FFFFFF;
            --text-primary: #0F172A;
            --text-secondary: #475569;
            --text-muted: #94A3B8;
            --border: #E2E8F0;
            --radius: 14px;
            --font: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        }

        /* ============================================================
        BASE
        ============================================================ */
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font);
            background: var(--bg-base);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.7;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
            font-family: var(--font);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* ============================================================
        UTILITIES
        ============================================================ */
        .text-teal {
            color: var(--teal) !important;
        }

        .text-accent {
            color: var(--accent) !important;
        }

        .btn-primary-custom {
            background: var(--teal);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: .7rem 1.7rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: .95rem;
            letter-spacing: .01em;
            transition: background .25s, transform .2s, box-shadow .25s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .4rem;
        }

        .btn-primary-custom:hover {
            background: var(--teal-dark);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.28);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .btn-outline-custom {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--teal);
            border: 2px solid var(--teal);
            padding: .65rem 1.65rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: .95rem;
            transition: background .25s, color .25s, transform .2s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .4rem;
        }

        .btn-outline-custom:hover {
            background: var(--teal);
            color: #fff;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .section-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--teal-light);
            color: var(--teal);
            border: 1px solid rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.25);
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: .75rem;
            letter-spacing: .12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: .3rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.18;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .divider-line {
            width: 54px;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--teal);
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 1.2rem 0 1.8rem;
        }

        /* ============================================================
        NAVBAR
        ============================================================ */
        .navbar-custom {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .93);
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: .85rem 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: box-shadow .3s;
        }

        .navbar-custom.scrolled {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, .07);
        }

        .navbar-brand-text {
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            color: var(--text-primary) !important;
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
        }

        .navbar-brand-text span {
            color: var(--teal);
        }

        .nav-link-custom {
            color: var(--text-secondary) !important;
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: .93rem;
            padding: .4rem .85rem !important;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: color .2s, background .2s;
        }

        .nav-link-custom:hover {
            color: var(--text-primary) !important;
            background: var(--bg-subtle);
        }

        .nav-link-custom.active-nav {
            color: var(--teal) !important;
        }

        /* ============================================================
        HERO
        ============================================================ */
        .hero-section {
            position: relative;
            padding: 100px 0 80px;
            background: var(--bg-alt);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 700px;
            height: 700px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.09) 0%, transparent 68%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            top: -220px;
            right: -180px;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-section::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.07) 0%, transparent 68%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            bottom: -100px;
            left: -80px;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .5rem;
            background: var(--accent-light);
            border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, .35);
            color: #92400E;
            font-size: .82rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: .35rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .hero-headline {
            font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.5vw, 3.7rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -.03em;
            margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .hero-headline .line-teal {
            color: var(--teal);
        }

        .hero-sub {
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 520px;
            margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 2.6rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hero-stat-num {
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .hero-stat-label {
            font-size: .8rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* Mockup */
        @keyframes floatY {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-12px);
            }
        }

        .hero-mockup-wrap {
            z-index: 1;
            animation: floatY 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .hero-mockup {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .mockup-bar {
            background: var(--bg-subtle);
            padding: .7rem 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .mockup-dot {
            width: 11px;
            height: 11px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .mockup-dot-red {
            background: #ff5f57;
        }

        .mockup-dot-yellow {
            background: #ffbd2e;
        }

        .mockup-dot-green {
            background: #28c840;
        }

        .mockup-body {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            min-height: 290px;
        }

        .dash-sidebar {
            background: var(--teal-light);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1rem .8rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.18);
        }

        .dash-nav-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .6rem;
            padding: .5rem .7rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: .8rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: .3rem;
        }

        .dash-nav-item.active {
            background: var(--teal);
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .dash-metric-card {
            background: var(--bg-subtle);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: .9rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .dash-metric-num {
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--teal);
        }

        .dash-metric-label {
            font-size: .72rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .dash-bar {
            height: 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: .4rem;
            background: var(--border);
        }

        .dash-bar-fill {
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background: var(--teal);
        }

        /* ============================================================
        FEATURES
        ============================================================ */
        .features-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: var(--bg-subtle);
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--surface-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem;
            height: 100%;
            transition: transform .25s, border-color .25s, box-shadow .25s;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            border-color: var(--teal);
            box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.12);
        }

        .feature-icon-wrap {
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: var(--teal-light);
            border: 1px solid rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.2);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--teal);
            margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: .4rem;
        }

        .feature-desc {
            font-size: .88rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.65;
        }

        /* ============================================================
        HOW IT WORKS
        ============================================================ */
        .how-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: var(--bg-alt);
        }

        .timeline-wrap {
            position: relative;
        }

        .timeline-line {
            position: absolute;
            left: 36px;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--teal), transparent);
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .timeline-line {
                left: 50%;
                transform: translateX(-50%);
            }
        }

        .timeline-step {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.6rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .step-number {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 72px;
            height: 72px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #fff;
            border: 2px solid var(--teal);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--teal);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px var(--teal-light);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .step-content {
            background: var(--surface-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .step-content h4 {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: .4rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .step-content p {
            font-size: .9rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* ============================================================
        PLANS
        ============================================================ */
        .plans-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: var(--bg-subtle);
        }

        .plan-card {
            background: var(--surface-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2.2rem 1.8rem;
            height: 100%;
            transition: transform .25s, box-shadow .25s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .plan-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
        }

        .plan-card.featured {
            border: 2px solid var(--teal);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.15);
        }

        .plan-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1.2rem;
            right: 1.2rem;
            background: var(--teal);
            color: #fff;
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: .72rem;
            letter-spacing: .06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: .25rem .8rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
        }

        .plan-name {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: .95rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: .09em;
            color: var(--teal);
            margin-bottom: .6rem;
        }

        .plan-price {
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: .3rem;
        }

        .plan-price sup {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            vertical-align: super;
            margin-right: .1rem;
        }

        .plan-period {
            font-size: .82rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .plan-divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin: 1.3rem 0;
        }

        .plan-feature {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: .6rem;
            font-size: .88rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: .65rem;
        }

        .plan-feature .bi {
            color: var(--teal);
            font-size: 1rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: .1rem;
        }

        .plan-feature.disabled {
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .plan-feature.disabled .bi {
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* ============================================================
        ABOUT
        ============================================================ */
        .about-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: var(--bg-alt);
        }

        .about-card {
            background: var(--bg-subtle);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 1.6rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 1rem;
            height: 100%;
            transition: box-shadow .2s;
        }

        .about-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.1);
        }

        .about-icon {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            background: var(--teal-light);
            border: 1px solid rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--teal);
        }

        .about-card h5 {
            font-size: .98rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: .3rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .about-card p {
            font-size: .86rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* ============================================================
        CONTACT
        ============================================================ */
        .contact-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: var(--bg-subtle);
        }

        .contact-form {
            background: var(--surface-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2.5rem 2.2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
        }

        .form-control-custom {
            background: var(--bg-subtle) !important;
            border: 1px solid var(--border) !important;
            color: var(--text-primary) !important;
            border-radius: 10px !important;
            padding: .75rem 1rem !important;
            font-family: var(--font) !important;
            font-size: .93rem !important;
            transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s !important;
        }

        .form-control-custom::placeholder {
            color: var(--text-muted) !important;
        }

        .form-control-custom:focus {
            border-color: var(--teal) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(93, 87, 244, 0.12) !important;
            outline: none !important;
            background: #fff !important;
        }

        .form-label-custom {
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: .84rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            letter-spacing: .02em;
            margin-bottom: .4rem;
            display: block;
        }

        /* ============================================================
        FOOTER
        ============================================================ */
        .footer {
            background: var(--text-primary);
            padding: 64px 0 28px;
        }

        .footer-brand {
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .footer-brand span {
            color: var(--teal);
        }

        .footer-desc {
            font-size: .88rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            max-width: 260px;
            line-height: 1.75;
            margin-top: .8rem;
        }

        .footer-heading {
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: .75rem;
            letter-spacing: .12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .footer-link {
            display: block;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
            font-size: .88rem;
            margin-bottom: .55rem;
            transition: color .2s;
        }

        .footer-link:hover {
            color: var(--teal);
        }

        .social-icon {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 38px;
            height: 38px;
            border-radius: 9px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background .2s, color .2s;
            margin-right: .5rem;
        }

        .social-icon:hover {
            background: var(--teal);
            color: #fff;
            border-color: var(--teal);
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
            margin-top: 3rem;
            padding-top: 1.4rem;
            font-size: .82rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
        }

        /* ============================================================
        SCROLL REVEAL
        ============================================================ */
        [data-fade] {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(24px);
            transition: opacity .65s ease, transform .65s ease;
        }

        [data-fade].visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: none;
        }

        /* ============================================================
        RESPONSIVE
        ============================================================ */
        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            .hero-section {
                padding: 70px 0 50px;
            }

            .hero-stats {
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .hero-mockup-wrap {
                margin-top: 3rem;
                animation: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="navbar-custom navbar navbar-expand-lg" id="navbar">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand navbar-brand-text" href="#">
            <i class="bi bi-heart-pulse-fill text-teal me-1"></i>System Home <span>Pet</span>
        </a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler border-0" type="button"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navMain"
                style="color:var(--text-secondary);">
            <i class="bi bi-list fs-4"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navMain">
            <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto gap-1">
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link-custom nav-link" href="#inicio">Início</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link-custom nav-link" href="#recursos">Recursos</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link-custom nav-link" href="#planos">Planos</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link-custom nav-link" href="#quem-somos">Quem Somos</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link-custom nav-link" href="#contato">Contato</a></li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/cadastro-estabelecimento" class="btn btn-primary-custom ms-lg-3 mt-2 mt-lg-0">
                Começar Agora <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>
<section class="hero-section" id="inicio">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="hero-badge">
                    <i class="bi bi-lightning-charge-fill"></i>
                    Gestão completa em uma plataforma
                </div>
                <h1 class="hero-headline">
                    O sistema completo para<br/>
                    <span class="line-teal">Pet Shops</span> &amp;<br/>
                    Clínicas Veterinárias
                </h1>
                <p class="hero-sub">
                    Centralize agendamentos, prontuários, financeiro, estoque e muito mais.
                    Uma solução moderna pensada para quem trabalha com o cuidado dos pets.
                </p>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                    <a href="/cadastro-estabelecimento" class="btn btn-primary-custom">
                        Começar Agora <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#planos" class="btn btn-outline-custom">Ver Planos</a>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-stats">
                    <div>
                        <div class="hero-stat-num">+2.400</div>
                        <div class="hero-stat-label">Estabelecimentos ativos</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
